{"tid":591241,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無ching試過發夢個陣喊？？😢","createTime":"2018-03-13T10:46:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T11:49:05.000Z","uid":5190,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c0c1649f9a4ce6c1fb7b1b661aa6084e74d415ea","tid":591241,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:46:18.000Z","msg":"話說 最近有個親人走咗 係好親個隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個心一直都好唔舒服 一直都好想喊出黎<br />\n想自己舒服啲 但唔知點解 即使我幾想喊都好 我都係喊唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n前幾日發咗個夢 夢見返佢 我感覺到我係夢入面係咁喊 有喊緊個種心痛嘅感覺 喊咗好多次<br />\n<br />\n醒咗之後 個人好似舒服咗啲...<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能男兒淚 真係難流啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c5c68ad98394e76f16118081528dd0a91b3fa6","tid":591241,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:50:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22770ae62b6fb04aad6821857b95188142018f48","tid":591241,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:50:38.000Z","msg":"有掛，anyway<br />\n<br />\n唔知講乜好，唔好介意"},{"pid":"f0e68b9e24df63f8e5a7db3365ab339a34920a75","tid":591241,"uid":132847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:51:47.000Z","msg":"有 都係同親人有關 醒嗰陣個枕頭濕嘅 眼入面仲有眼淚"},{"pid":"aaf9292e76bcaab82ec5e9c892be644738000be9","tid":591241,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04c5c68ad98394e76f16118081528dd0a91b3fa6","tid":591241,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:50:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:51:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcdfdd21822a4df0e45be71ba18becd8cc6d3086","tid":591241,"uid":117301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc